&lt;h1 id=&#34;variable-變數&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#variable-變數&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Variable 變數&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;note warning no-icon&#34;&gt;
